        "created_at": "2019-11-27T22:25:19.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"6\" data-topic=\"156451\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Do you guys like the Sorbes?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yes.  I have liked every wine I have had from Jouan.  Now, some people compare Jouan to Truchot and I do not think that Jouan\u2019s wines are in anywhere near the same class as the wines from Truchot, but they are excellent Burgundies.</p>",
